{
  "stem": "22979.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only the top was light where you could stretch out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the two down, you had to lie down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not I-- I jumped to the third floor-- and with whom we were good friends-- about nine of us-- because to one [NON-ENGLISH], where only three or four people could sleep, we were assigned 10.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because in one barrack were 1,000 inmates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the upper [NON-ENGLISH] was lucky-- but no mattress, no straw, and no blanket-- only the worn-out Russian uniforms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We, you know, when we came to-- to the camp, had to live in-- in our working place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We could change to [NON-ENGLISH] clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we had to leave them there and then put up our uniforms, the Russian-- when we went back to camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you know, there we changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they enclosed our uniform at the working place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they enclosed the-- the Russian uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when we went back to the camp, we had to change.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we came to Birkenau still in our Russian uniforms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we didn't go to work, only then after we moved there, after maybe two, three days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this time, we were already close to 50,000, or maybe more, women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But people, what they did-- many people in Auschwitz, on the second floor, jumped to their death.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Many committed suicide going to the high voltage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In the morning, you see like a Christmas tree.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "People you know, charred, dark, hanging on to-- to-- to the, you know, high voltage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And when we came to Birkenau, it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- in Auschwitz, down in the basement, I said it was dripping, the water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No toilets.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Latrine was 200 feet behind the barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
